{
  "stem": "21978.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We have been working under the Germans in the Jewish orphanage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we are saboteuring our jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we are not allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We are Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We can't just choose whatever to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We have our masters to listen to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we have to be-- we had to leave Annetta there and go back to the orphanage and work there, and wait for our turn.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Fortunately, Annetta, when she left for Theresienstadt, was able to smuggle through some Czech police, gendarme, some note that we knew that she's in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because transports were going through Theresienstadt, and they were going away from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We knew that they are going to east-- people from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But we didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we didn't know their fate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We didn't know much about Theresienstadt at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We just were told that Theresienstadt is a place where the Jews will be all living together happy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they will work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we didn't know much about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My husband and I got a call in December, in '42, to assemble.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were sent to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And while Annetta and I were separated, she has made friends in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She started to work as a nursing aide in a children's hospital at the infectious disease.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And young, she made friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she made friends with Ghettowache.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Jewish people have been the guardians of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The establishment was led-- led by-- the administration was by Jewish elders in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the policing was done by Jewish people-- Jewish Ghettowache-- ghetto police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And Annetta made friends with one of them and told him, when the transports come from Prague, my sister might can just as well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And she looks like me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And you-- you watch out for her.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
